---
title: Mozzarella-Stuffed Meatball Bake with Cavatappi and a Crispy Panko Topping
description: Sure, you’ve heard of a cheese-stuffed burger, but a cheese-stuffed meatball?! Now that’s next-level culinary innovation. Tuscan-spiced ground beef is wrapped around pieces of fresh mozzarella and then baked. While they’re in the oven, you’ll be boiling cavatappi and whipping up a from-scratch tomato sauce. Everything is stirred together, then topped with buttery panko and more fresh mozzarella. A trip under the broiler transforms the topping into crunchy, melty perfection. *Now that’s a cheesy meatball!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mozzarella-stuffed-meatball-bake-496f6e24.jpg
